sentences: Bruce MacGregor is a Scottish fiddler and broadcaster who founded Blazin' Fiddles in 1998, and currently presents  Travelling Folk on BBC Radio Scotland.
Bruce MacGregor is a Scottish fiddler and broadcaster who founded Blazin' Fiddles in 1998, and currently presents  Travelling Folk on BBC Radio Scotland.
Bruce MacGregor was born in Inverness in 1970.
MacGregor started working at BBC Radio Scotland in 1994 as a researcher before becoming a producer and presenter.
